text: Levente Apagyi (born 18 December 1993) is a Hungarian sprint canoeist.Profile He won a medal at the 2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships.2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships results ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male canoeists Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in kayak Category:Canoeists from Budapest
